Package seng202.group7.data

Class DataAccessor

java.lang.Object
seng202.group7.data.DataAccessor
public final class DataAccessor
extends java.lang.Object
This class works to link the SQLite database with our java application. It gets key data from the database during the runtime of the application.
Author:
Jack McCorkindale, John Elliott, Shaylin Simadari, Sam McMillan
